{
  "text": "The simulations have been conducted in MATLAB R2015a to compare the performance of the proposed algorithms with three other existing algorithms: ACO-CA [CITATION_1] , Tree-Cluster [CITATION_2] and LEACH-FD [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
